---
title: What home projects really cost in DFW
description: Researched cost ranges for home repairs and upgrades across North Texas. Updated regularly, no lead-gen forms, no inflated "free quote" funnels.
layout: base.njk
---
<section class="hero">
  <h1>What home repairs and upgrades actually cost in North Texas</h1>
  <p>Researched ranges, updated regularly, no lead-gen forms. We aggregate contractor price lists, permit data, and published industry pricing for the Dallas–Fort Worth market so you can walk into a bid knowing what's normal.</p>
  <p class="hero-links"><a href="/methodology/">How we build these numbers</a></p>
</section>

{% if collections.guides.length %}
  {% set cats = [] %}
  {% for g in collections.guides %}
    {% if g.data.category and cats.indexOf(g.data.category) == -1 %}
      {% set _ = cats.push(g.data.category) %}
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}

  {% for cat in cats %}
  <section class="cat-group">
    <h2>{{ cat }}</h2>
    <div class="cards">
      {% for g in collections.guides %}
        {% if g.data.category == cat %}
        <a class="card" href="{{ g.url }}">
          <h3>{{ g.data.title }}</h3>
          <p>{{ g.data.description }}</p>
          <span class="updated">Updated {{ g.data.updated | readableDate }}</span>
        </a>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
  {% endfor %}

  {% set uncategorized = [] %}
  {% for g in collections.guides %}
    {% if not g.data.category %}{% set _ = uncategorized.push(g) %}{% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
  {% if uncategorized.length %}
  <section class="cat-group">
    <h2>More guides</h2>
    <div class="cards">
      {% for g in uncategorized %}
      <a class="card" href="{{ g.url }}">
        <h3>{{ g.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ g.data.description }}</p>
        <span class="updated">Updated {{ g.data.updated | readableDate }}</span>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
  {% endif %}
{% else %}
<section class="cat-group">
  <p class="empty-note">First cost guides are in research now. Check back soon, or read <a href="/methodology/">how we price</a> in the meantime.</p>
</section>
{% endif %}
